MLOps Lifecycle Five Phases. Circular flow: 1) DEVELOP: Prompts, Model Configs, Data Pipelines, Service Code. 2) TEST: Golden Datasets, Prompt Tests, Cost/Latency Checks. 3) DEPLOY: Versioned Releases, Canary Deployments, Rollbacks. 4) MONITOR: Drift, Feedback, Costs, Performance. 5) IMPROVE: Rules, Data, Prompts Iterate -> back to DEVELOP. Arrows forming circle. Center: "Version Control (Git, DVC, Model Cards)". German labels.